Package org.gvsig.topology.ui

Interface Summary
ITopologyContentProvider All classes that implements this interface could provide the needed content to create a topology: vectorial layers a view's map context. topology rules. A panel where the user is entering its options, or even a topology could provides this info.
LayerJComboBox.LayerFilter Interface to filter layers in the combo box.
LayerSelectionPanel.LayerSelectionListener Subclasses of this interface listen for events launched by this control
TopologyRulesPanel.RuleSelectionListener Interface that must be implemented by all of these classes interested in listening adding or removing rules events.
 

Class Summary
LayerJComboBox JComboBox to show the layers of a FLayers instance.
LayerSelectionPanel This panel manages the selection of layers in TOC.
LayersInTocPanel Panel which shows toc layers with a check box to select or unselect many of them.
NewTopologyRulePanel GUI component to create new topology rules instances.
NewTopologyWizard Wizard to create new topologies.
TopologyErrorPanel Panel to show topology errors stored in a ITopologyErrorContainer.
TopologyPropertiesPanel Panel which shows properties of a given topology
TopologyRulesPanel Panel to show topology rules of a topology
UpdateTopologyInTocLayerCollectionListener LayerCollectionListener which updates the toc.
